# Synthetic data generation
#
# Only required for the FIRST run of `make seed-synthetic` on a fresh machine
# (or after deleting seeds/scripts/llm_fixtures/). Subsequent runs read from
# committed LLM fixtures and never call the Anthropic API — that's why CI does
# not need this key.
#
# Get a key from: https://console.anthropic.com/
# Cost cap for first-run generation: $5.00 (enforced by the generator).
#
ANTHROPIC_API_KEY=sk-ant-...
